  sign
  Builtin Function



      [1mSynopsis[0m
        Return the sign of [4mA[0m

      [1mSyntax[0m
        sign ( [4mA[24m )

      [1mDescription[0m

        For real scalar argument, sign returns:


          1 if A > 0



          0 if A == 0



          -1 if A < 0


     For a complex scalar sign returns:


          A ./ abs (A)


     sign performs its operation on real and complex matrices in an
     element by element fashion.































